    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Expatriation or prolonged absence from one's native land, endured by compulsion or by circumstances, or voluntarily undergone for any purpose. For the legal state of having been forcibly exiled, use "banishment."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
